Package: VisualSHIELD
Title: Shiny module to seamlessly analyze Opal (https://www.obiba.org/pages/products/opal/) and dbNP (https://www.dbnp.org/) remote data through the privacy-aware DataSHIELD (https://www.datashield.ac.uk/) analysis package 
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Danilo",
           family = "Tomasoni",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "tomasoni@cosbi.eu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8427-4230"))
Description: This package contains a shiny module, that means that it can be used in another custom shiny app. The module is exposed through the VisualSHIELDUI and the VisualSHIELDServer functions. The module builds a user-frendly web-UI to analyze remote data hosted on opal servers. It allows also to port dbNP data to Opal, in such a way that also dbNP data can be used in the analysis.
